\c 96
\s Nyika yose ngairumbidze Jehovha Mutongi mukuru
\p
\v 1 Imbirai Jehovha rwiyo rutsva; Imbirai Jehovha, pasi pose.
\v 2 Imbirai Jehovha, rumbidzai zita rake; Paridzai kuponesa kwake zuva rimwe nerimwe.
\v 3 Dudzirai kubwinya kwake pakati pavahedheni, Mabasa ake, anoshamisa pakati pendudzi dzose.
\v 4 Nokuti Jehovha mukuru, anofanira kurumbidzwa kwazvo; Anofanira kutyiwa kupfuura vamwari vose.
\v 5 Nokuti vamwari vose vendudzi zvifananidzo hazvo; Asi Jehovha akaita kudenga-denga.
\v 6 Kukudzwa noumambo zviri pamberi pake; Simba nokunaka zviri panzvimbo yake tsvene.
\v 7 Ipai Jehovha, imi mhuri dzavanhu, Ipai Jehovha kukudzwa nesimba.
\v 8 Ipai Jehovha kukudzwa kunofanira zita rake; Uyai nechipiriso, mupinde muvazhe dzake.
\v 9 Namatai kuna Jehovha nenguva tsvene; Pasi pose bvunda pamberi pake.
\v 10 Itiyi pakati pavahedheni, Jehovha ndiye anobata hushe; Nyikawo yakasirnbiswa, kuti irege kuzununguswa;
\s Iye achatonga vanhu zvakarurama."
\p
\v 11 Kudenga-denga ngakufare, kwazvo; Gungwa ngaritinhire, nezvose zviri mukati maro;
\p
\v 12 Sango ngarive nomufaro,
\s nezvose zviri mukati maro;
\s Ipapo miti yose yedondo ichaimba nomufaro;
\p
\v 13 Pamberi paJehovha, nokuti anouya; Nokuti anouya kuzotonga pasi;
\s kdkatowp. kxyW,a. fakuwama., Nendudzi nokutendeka kwake.
